OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen it will be dry and clear with
OL,8,Flight winds. A chilly night with a
OL,9,Fslight frost in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FIt will be dry throughout
OL,12,Fthe day with lengthy spells of
OL,13,Fsunshine. Light and variable winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,16,Fmostly dry and settled but more in the
OL,17,Fway of cloud likely over the weekend
OL,18,Fwith the odd spot of rain possible.
OL,19,FLight winds.
